:[6],"tags":[416,114,532,20,287,28],"class_list":["post-36200","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-manners-adab","tag-prayer-for-rain-salat-al-istisqa","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-rain-al-matr","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9pS","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36193,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/16\/salat-al-istisqa\/","url_meta":{"origin":36200,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Istisqa: The Prophet prays and supplicates for rain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Zayd reported: I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, one day go out to prayer for rain. He turned his back to the people and faced the Qiblah and supplicated, then he turns his cloak inside out, then he prayed two cycles for us while\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25489,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/30\/dua-beneficial-rain\/","url_meta":{"origin":36200,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: O Allah, make it blessed rain for us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saw rain, he would say, \u201cO Allah, a beneficial downpour.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1032 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u064a\u0651\u0650\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064b\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6544,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/tawassul-call-upon-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":36200,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawassul: Not calling on the Prophet after his death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: If a drought became threatening, Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, would ask Al-'Abbas ibn Abdul Muttalib to supplicate for Allah to send rain. Umar would say, \u201cO Allah, we used to ask our Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to supplicate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34009,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/dua-for-a-windy-storm\/","url_meta":{"origin":36200,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rain: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for a windy storm","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, if there was a windy storm, he would say, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for its good, the good within it, and the good for which it was sent. I seek refuge in You from its evil, the evil within\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26041,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/moderate-dignified-laughter\/","url_meta":{"origin":36200,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Laughter: The Prophet was moderate, dignified in laughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I never saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, laughing so hard that one could see the back of his throat. Rather, he would only smile. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4551,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 899 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34093,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/salat-at-home-rain\/","url_meta":{"o